  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3377907">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3377907/" class="title-link">国破山河在，青山为证，忠魂鉴史~</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3377907"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/8027178/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/8027178/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">天命瘦狐</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-30"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-30 09:50:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3377907_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作者以身份之便，从日本国内的资料、日本老兵的回忆和珍贵的、甚至是未见于史料的老照片，将日本人眼中的抗战中国一一展现，中国军队的勇猛、中国百姓的顽强，是日本人不愿言表的噩梦。而瞒报、少报伤亡，夸张战果的拙略手段被日本人使用的炉火纯青~让人发笑~ 总之，此书很值~

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            山东画报出版社2010版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3377907_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3377907_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
